<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>정지안 | Performance Marketer</title>
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/orioncactus/pretendard/dist/web/static/pretendard.css" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root {
  --blue:    #4285f4;
  --blue-lt: #EAF1FE;
  --blue-dk: #2563c4;
  --ink:     #111111;
  --ink2:    #333333;
  --muted:   #888888;
  --border:  #E8E8E8;
  --bg:      #F7F7F7;
  --white:   #FFFFFF;
  --imsg-bg: #E9E9EB;
  --imsg-blue: #4285f4;
}

* { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
html { scroll-behavior:smooth; }
body { font-family:'Pretendard',-apple-system,sans-serif; background:var(--white); color:var(--ink); line-height:1.7; cursor:none; }
a, button { cursor:none; }

/* ── CURSOR ── */
.cursor { width:8px; height:8px; background:var(--blue); border-radius:50%; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:9999; }
.cursor-ring { width:30px; height:30px; border:1.5px solid var(--blue); border-radius:50%; position:fixed; top:0; left:0; pointer-events:none; z-index:9998; opacity:0.4; transition:width .2s,height .2s; }

/* ── NAV ── */
nav {
  position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:60px;
  padding:0 48px; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
  background:rgba(255,255,255,0.92); backdrop-filter:blur(16px);
  border-bottom:1px solid transparent; z-index:100; transition:border-color .3s;
}
nav.scrolled { border-color:var(--border); }
.nav-name { font-size:15px; font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); }
.nav-name span { color:var(--blue); }
.nav-links { display:flex; gap:28px; }
.nav-links a { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); text-decoration:none; transition:color .2s; }
.nav-links a:hover { color:var(--ink); }

/* ══ HERO 1 — FULLSCREEN TYPO ══════════════════════════════ */
#hero-typo {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; flex-direction: column; justify-content: center;
  padding: 100px 10vw 80px;
  background: var(--white);
  position: relative; overflow: hidden;
}
#hero-typo::before {
  content:'';
  position:absolute; inset:0;
  background-image:linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:48px 48px; opacity:0.3;
  pointer-events:none;
}
.typo-eyebrow {
  font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase;
  color:var(--blue); font-weight:600; margin-bottom:20px;
  opacity:0; animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s forwards;
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.typo-headline {
  font-size: clamp(40px, 7vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 800;
  color: var(--ink);
  letter-spacing: -0.04em;
  line-height: 1.2;
  margin-bottom: 32px;
  opacity:0; animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s forwards;
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.typo-headline .break { display:block; }
.typo-headline .accent { color:var(--blue); }
.typo-sub {
  font-size: clamp(15px, 1.8vw, 20px);
  color: var(--muted);
  font-weight: 400;
  line-height: 1.6;
  max-width: 520px;
  margin-bottom: 48px;
  opacity:0; animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.35s forwards;
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.typo-sub strong { color:var(--ink2); font-weight:500; }
.typo-stats {
  display:flex; gap:0; flex-wrap:wrap;
  max-width:560px;
  border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; overflow:hidden;
  opacity:0; animation:fadeUp 0.6s 0.45s forwards;
  position:relative; z-index:1;
}
.typo-stat { flex:1; min-width:110px; padding:18px 20px; border-right:1px solid var(--border); background:var(--white); }
.typo-stat:last-child { border-right:none; }
.typo-stat-num { font-size:26px; font-weight:800; color:var(--ink); letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1; margin-bottom:3px; }
.typo-stat-num span { color:var(--blue); }
.typo-stat-label { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); }
.scroll-hint {
  position:absolute; bottom:36px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:8px;
  opacity:0; animation:fadeUp 0.5s 1.2s forwards;
  z-index:1;
}
.scroll-hint span { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
.scroll-hint-arrow { animation:arrowBounce 1.5s infinite; font-size:16px; color:var(--muted); }
@keyframes arrowBounce { 0%,100%{transform:translateY(0)} 50%{transform:translateY(6px)} }

/* ══ HERO 2 — iMESSAGE ══════════════════════════════════════ */
#hero-imsg {
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  padding: 80px 24px;
  background: var(--bg);
  position:relative;
}
/* Mac window */
.mac-window {
  width:100%; max-width:440px;
  background:#fff;
  border-radius:16px;
  box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.12), 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  overflow:hidden;
}
/* Title bar */
.mac-titlebar {
  background:#F0F0F0;
  padding:12px 16px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
  border-bottom:1px solid #E0E0E0;
}
.mac-dots { display:flex; gap:6px; }
.mac-dot { width:12px; height:12px; border-radius:50%; }
.mac-dot.red{background:#FF5F57} .mac-dot.yellow{background:#FEBC2E} .mac-dot.green{background:#28C840}
.mac-title-center {
  flex:1; display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:4px;
}
.mac-avatar-center {
  width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%;
  background:var(--blue-lt);
  display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;
  font-size:12px; font-weight:700; color:var(--blue);
  overflow:hidden; flex-shrink:0;
  border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
  box-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}
.mac-avatar-center img { width:100%; height:100%; object-fit:cover; object-position:center top; }
.mac-contact-name { font-size:13px; font-weight:600; color:var(--ink); }
/* Chat area */
.chat-area {
  padding:16px 16px 12px;
  height:320px;
  background:#fff;
  display:flex;
  flex-direction:column;
  overflow:hidden;
  position:relative;
}
.chat-inner {
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:6px;
  margin-top:auto;
}
.chat-date { text-align:center; font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:8px; }
/* Bubbles — right only (outgoing) */
.bubble-row { display:flex; justify-content:flex-end; }
.bubble {
  max-width:78%;
  padding:10px 15px;
  border-radius:18px;
  border-bottom-right-radius:4px;
  font-size:14px; line-height:1.55;
  background:#4285f4;
  color:#fff;
  opacity:0;
  transform:translateY(16px);
  transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
  flex-shrink:0;
}
.bubble.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
/* typing */
.bubble-row.typing-row { justify-content:flex-end; }
.bubble-row.typing-row.hidden { display:none !important; }
.typing-bubble {
  background:#4285f4; border-radius:18px; border-bottom-right-radius:4px;
  padding:12px 16px;
  display:flex; align-items:center; gap:4px; width:58px;
  opacity:0; transform:translateY(16px);
  transition:opacity 0.3s ease, transform 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.46, 0.45, 0.94);
}
.typing-bubble.visible { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
.dot-b { width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.7); animation:bounce 1.2s infinite; }
.dot-b:nth-child(2){animation-delay:.2s} .dot-b:nth-child(3){animation-delay:.4s}
@keyframes bounce{0%,60%,100%{transform:translateY(0)}30%{transform:translateY(-6px)}}
/* input bar */
.chat-input-bar { padding:10px 12px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); display:flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; background:#fff; }
.chat-input-fake { flex:1; background:#E9E9EB; border-radius:20px; padding:8px 14px; font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); }
.chat-send-btn { width:30px; height:30px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blue); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; border:none; }
.chat-send-btn svg { width:14px; height:14px; fill:#fff; }

/* scroll down from imsg */
.imsg-scroll-hint {
  position:absolute; bottom:32px; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%);
  display:flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center; gap:6px;
  opacity:0; transition:opacity 0.5s;
}
.imsg-scroll-hint.show { opacity:1; }
.imsg-scroll-hint span { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; }
.ish-arrow { animation:arrowBounce 1.5s infinite; font-size:16px; color:var(--muted); }

/* ══ SECTION COMMON ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
/* ══ SECTION COMMON ══════════════════════════════════════════ */
.section-wrap { padding:96px 10vw; }
.section-wrap.bg-gray { background:var(--bg); }
.section-wrap.bg-dark { background:var(--ink); }

.section-kicker { font-size:11px; letter-spacing:0.16em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue); font-weight:600; margin-bottom:10px; }
.section-title { font-size:clamp(24px,3.5vw,40px); font-weight:800; color:var(--ink); letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:8px; }
.section-title.light { color:var(--white); }
.section-desc { font-size:14px; color:var(--muted); }
.section-desc.light { color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45); }
.section-top { margin-bottom:48px; }

/* ══ CASES ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.cases-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); gap:16px; }

.case-card {
  background:var(--white); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px;
  padding:28px; cursor:pointer; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
  transition:box-shadow .25s, transform .25s, border-color .25s;
}
.case-card:hover { box-shadow:0 8px 40px rgba(66,133,244,.12); transform:translateY(-3px); border-color:var(--blue); }
.case-card::after { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:0; right:0; height:3px; background:var(--blue); transform:scaleX(0); transform-origin:left; transition:transform .3s; }
.case-card:hover::after { transform:scaleX(1); }

.case-tag { display:inline-block; font-size:10px; font-weight:600; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; padding:3px 9px; border-radius:4px; margin-bottom:14px; }
.t-beauty { background:var(--blue-lt); color:var(--blue); }
.t-data   { background:#EDF5FF; color:#2563c4; }
.t-create { background:#FFF3E8; color:#C25A1A; }
.t-infra  { background:#F0FAF0; color:#1A7A3A; }
.t-org    { background:#F5F0FF; color:#5A2AC2; }

.case-num { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); position:absolute; top:28px; right:28px; }
.case-title { font-size:16px; font-weight:800; line-height:1.35; margin-bottom:8px; letter-spacing:-0.02em; }
.case-sub { font-size:12.5px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.6; margin-bottom:18px; }
.case-result { font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:var(--blue); letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1; }
.case-result-sub { font-size:11px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:3px; }
.case-more { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:5px; font-size:12px; font-weight:600; color:var(--blue); margin-top:16px; opacity:0; transform:translateX(-6px); transition:opacity .2s, transform .2s; }
.case-card:hover .case-more { opacity:1; transform:none; }

/* ══ ABOUT ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.about-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:72px; align-items:start; }
.about-body { font-size:15px; color:var(--ink2); line-height:1.8; margin-bottom:16px; }
.career-list { margin-top:36px; }
.career-item { display:flex; gap:16px; padding:16px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.c-dot { width:8px; height:8px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blue); margin-top:5px; flex-shrink:0; }
.c-dot.dim { background:var(--border); }
.c-co { font-weight:700; font-size:14px; }
.c-role { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:1px; }
.c-period { font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:2px; }

.strength-list { display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:12px; }
.strength-item { padding:22px 24px; background:var(--white); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:8px; border-left:3px solid var(--blue); transition:box-shadow .2s; }
.strength-item:hover { box-shadow:0 4px 20px rgba(66,133,244,.08); }
.s-title { font-weight:700; font-size:14px; margin-bottom:6px; }
.s-desc { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); line-height:1.65; }

/* ══ STACK ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.stack-groups { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr); gap:32px; }
.sg-label { font-size:11px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.12em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--muted); margin-bottom:12px; padding-bottom:10px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
.pills { display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px; }
.pill { font-size:12.5px; padding:7px 14px; border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:6px; color:var(--ink2); background:var(--white); transition:all .2s; }
.pill:hover { border-color:var(--blue); color:var(--blue); background:var(--blue-lt); }
.pill.hot { background:var(--blue-lt); border-color:var(--blue); color:var(--blue); font-weight:600; }

/* ══ CONTACT ══════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.contact-inner { max-width:560px; }
.contact-title { font-size:clamp(28px,4vw,48px); font-weight:800; color:var(--white); letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:12px; }
.contact-title span { color:var(--blue); }
.contact-sub { font-size:14px; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45); margin-bottom:36px; }
.contact-row { display:flex; gap:16px; flex-wrap:wrap; }
.contact-link { display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:8px; padding:13px 24px; border:1.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,.15); border-radius:8px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.75); text-decoration:none; font-size:13px; font-weight:500; transition:all .2s; }
.contact-link:hover { border-color:var(--blue); color:#fff; background:rgba(66,133,244,.15); }

/* ══ MODAL ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.modal-overlay { position:fixed; inset:0; background:rgba(0,0,0,.55); backdrop-filter:blur(4px); z-index:1000; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; padding:24px; opacity:0; pointer-events:none; transition:opacity .25s; }
.modal-overlay.open { opacity:1; pointer-events:all; }
.modal { background:var(--white); border-radius:16px; max-width:720px; width:100%; max-height:85vh; overflow-y:auto; transform:translateY(24px) scale(.97); transition:transform .3s; position:relative; }
.modal-overlay.open .modal { transform:none; }
.modal-header { padding:36px 40px 24px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); position:sticky; top:0; background:var(--white); border-radius:16px 16px 0 0; z-index:1; }
.modal-tag { margin-bottom:10px; }
.modal-title { font-size:22px; font-weight:800; letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1.3; margin-bottom:6px; }
.modal-sub { font-size:13px; color:var(--muted); }
.modal-close { position:absolute; top:24px; right:24px; width:36px; height:36px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--bg); border:none; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; cursor:pointer; transition:background .2s; font-size:18px; color:var(--muted); }
.modal-close:hover { background:var(--border); }
.modal-body { padding:32px 40px 40px; }
.modal-result-banner { background:var(--blue-lt); border-radius:10px; padding:20px 24px; display:flex; gap:32px; flex-wrap:wrap; margin-bottom:32px; }
.mbr-num { font-size:32px; font-weight:800; color:var(--blue); letter-spacing:-0.03em; line-height:1; }
.mbr-label { font-size:12px; color:var(--blue-dk); margin-top:3px; }
.modal-section { margin-bottom:28px; }
.ms-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.14em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--blue); margin-bottom:10px; padding-bottom:8px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--blue-lt); }
.ms-text { font-size:14px; color:var(--ink2); line-height:1.8; }
.ms-text p { margin-bottom:10px; }
.ms-text p:last-child { margin-bottom:0; }
.ms-text strong { font-weight:700; color:var(--ink); }
.ms-ba { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:12px; margin-top:12px; }
.ba-box { padding:14px 16px; border-radius:8px; }
.ba-box.before { background:#FFF5F5; border:1px solid #FFDDDD; }
.ba-box.after  { background:var(--blue-lt); border:1px solid #C5D8FC; }
.ba-label { font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.1em; text-transform:uppercase; margin-bottom:6px; }
.ba-box.before .ba-label { color:#CC3333; }
.ba-box.after  .ba-label { color:var(--blue); }
.ba-text { font-size:13px; line-height:1.65; color:var(--ink2); }
.insight-list { list-style:none; }
.insight-list li { padding:10px 0 10px 16px; border-bottom:1px solid var(--bg); font-size:13.5px; color:var(--ink2); line-height:1.7; position:relative; }
.insight-list li::before { content:''; position:absolute; left:0; top:18px; width:5px; height:5px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--blue); }
.insight-list li:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
.highlight-box { background:var(--ink); border-radius:8px; padding:18px 20px; margin-top:16px; }
.hb-text { font-size:13.5px; color:rgba(255,255,255,.85); line-height:1.7; font-style:italic; }
.img-placeholder { background:var(--bg); border:2px dashed var(--border); border-radius:8px; padding:20px; text-align:center; margin-top:12px; color:var(--muted); font-size:12px; line-height:1.6; }
.img-placeholder strong { color:var(--ink2); display:block; margin-bottom:4px; }

/* ══ REVEAL ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ */
.reveal { opacity:0; transform:translateY(24px); transition:opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease; }
.reveal.visible { opacity:1; transform:none; }
.d1{transition-delay:.08s} .d2{transition-delay:.16s} .d3{transition-delay:.24s}

@keyframes fadeUp { from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)} to{opacity:1;transform:none} }

::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px} ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:var(--blue);border-radius:2px}

@media(max-width:900px){
  nav{padding:0 24px} .nav-links{display:none}
  .section-wrap{padding:72px 24px}
  .about-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
  .cases-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .stack-groups{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .ms-ba{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .modal-body{padding:24px} .modal-header{padding:24px 24px 16px}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="cursor" id="cursor"></div>
<div class="cursor-ring" id="cursorRing"></div>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav id="nav">
  <div class="nav-name">정지안<span>.</span></div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#cases">케이스</a>
    <a href="#about">소개</a>
    <a href="#stack">스택</a>
    <a href="#contact">연락</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══ HERO ══════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<!-- ══ HERO 1: FULLSCREEN TYPO ══════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="hero-typo">
  <div class="typo-eyebrow">Performance Marketing Lead · 5yr</div>
  <h1 class="typo-headline">
    <span class="break">기억에 남는 마케팅과</span>
    <span class="break"><span class="accent">지갑을 여는 마케팅</span>은</span>
    <span class="break">다르다.</span>
  </h1>
  <p class="typo-sub">
    <strong>전환이 안 되는 건 다 이유가 있다</strong> — 저는 그 이유를 쫓습니다.<br>
    월 5억 예산 · 30인 조직 · 뷰티·헬스케어·글로벌
  </p>
  <div class="typo-stats">
    <div class="typo-stat"><div class="typo-stat-num">5억<span>+</span></div><div class="typo-stat-label">월 최대 광고 예산</div></div>
    <div class="typo-stat"><div class="typo-stat-num">30<span>명</span></div><div class="typo-stat-label">직접 관리 팀 규모</div></div>
    <div class="typo-stat"><div class="typo-stat-num">5<span>yr</span></div><div class="typo-stat-label">퍼포먼스 마케팅</div></div>
    <div class="typo-stat"><div class="typo-stat-num">4<span>개</span></div><div class="typo-stat-label">글로벌 시장</div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-hint">
    <span>scroll</span>
    <div class="scroll-hint-arrow">↓</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ══ HERO 2: iMESSAGE ═══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section id="hero-imsg">
  <div class="mac-window">
    <div class="mac-titlebar">
      <div class="mac-dots">
        <div class="mac-dot red"></div>
        <div class="mac-dot yellow"></div>
